ion-store/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md`","oldString":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Spec Draft)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: \n\n- [ ] **1.1** \n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: \n\n- [ ] **2.1** \n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Validation\n\n- [ ] **3.1** `go build ./pkg/store/...` — successful compilation\n- [ ] **3.2** `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` — all unit tests pass\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md`"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md\n===================================================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md\n+++ /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md\n@@ -2,36 +2,47 @@\n \n **Module:** pkg/store  \n **Language:** Go  \n **Size:** S  \n-**Stage:** ST-1 (Spec Draft)\n+**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n \n ---\n \n-## Phase 1: \n+## Phase 1: Core Interface & Errors\n \n-- [ ] **1.1** \n+- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/store/store.go` — define `Store` interface with all 9 methods per design spec\n+- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/store/errors.go` — define `ErrNotFound` error variable\n+- [ ] **1.3** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n \n ---\n \n-## Phase 2: \n+## Phase 2: Implementation\n \n-- [ ] **2.1** \n+- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/store/singleton.go` — implement `Storage()`, `initStore()`, provider constants, singleton pattern\n+- [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/store/store_redis.go` — implement Redis store using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n+- [ ] **2.3** Create `pkg/store/store_valkey.go` — implement Valkey store using `github.com/valkey-io/valk